        "The **current path** (Part 1) uses the provided `optimal_tsp` file with exact pairwise distances and yields a tour length of **1325**. The path from Part 2.7 uses distances estimated by our ACO algorithm on the hard maze, then runs the GA on that distance matrix.\n",
